{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/removing-blue-box-whenever-tapping-or-clicking-elements","result":{"pageContext":{"id":1114,"date":"2021-08-16T01:53:02","date_gmt":"2021-08-16T01:53:02","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=1114"},"modified":"2021-08-16T02:03:39","modified_gmt":"2021-08-16T02:03:39","slug":"removing-blue-box-whenever-tapping-or-clicking-elements","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/removing-blue-box-whenever-tapping-or-clicking-elements/","title":{"rendered":"Removing blue box whenever tapping or clicking elements"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>You may have noticed before, especially on mobile devices, that if you press and hold a specific clickable element a blue box will appear around it. <br><br>This is a normal and expected behavior of most modern web browsers: this intended feature serves to help those with impaired vision to be able to differentiate from clickable to non-clickable elements. <br><br>Anyhow, if your website already has a well written and semantic code &#8211; like all official Shopify themes do from the get go -, this can be removed without causing any negative impacts to your visitors. <br><br>This is how you can quickly remove the blue background from clickable elements on your website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-locating-the-code-file-to-edit\">Locating the code file to edit</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>From your Shopify admin, navigate to <strong>Online Store</strong> > <strong>Themes </strong>> <strong>Actions </strong>> <strong>Edit Code</strong>.</li><li>Find the file named <strong>theme.liquid.</strong> You can type it on the search bar to ensure you select the correct one.</li><li>Inside this file, press CTRL + F (or CMD + F on Mac) and search for:<br><br><strong>&lt;/body></strong><br></li><li>Paste the following code <strong>before </strong>the <strong>&lt;/body></strong> line you found and save:<br><br>[gist]e48385c60ca48b5377dfed1819b66b8e[gist]<br></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1003\" height=\"703\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/image.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1128\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/image.png 1003w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/image-850x596.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/image-768x538.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1003px) 100vw, 1003px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And that&#8217;s it &#8211; you are all set!</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Quickly remove the blue background that appears on clickable elements. Works on every theme.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1121,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[9],"tags":[206],"image_alt":"","featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/blue_box-1-850x478.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/blue_box-1-200x200.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/blue_box-1-1200x675.png","categories_names":["Blog"],"acf":[],"tag_names":["all themes"],"featured_image_url":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/blue_box-1.png","featured_image_url_alt":"","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1114"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/comments?post=1114"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1114/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1132,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1114/revisions/1132"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media/1121"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media?parent=1114"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/categories?post=1114"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/tags?post=1114"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https://api.w.org/{rel}","templated":true}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["330429198","3356652627"]}